      <guid>https://mcjoi.github.io/macrotoolkit-xls/01003/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;script---value-format&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Script - Value format&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#script---value-format&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;number-format&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Number format&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#number-format&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;formatnum_normal&#34;&gt;&#xA;  formatNum_normal&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#formatnum_normal&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&amp;amp;fname=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.kakaocdn.net%2Fdna%2FoW5yo%2FbtsPNgF47CO%2FAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAADVo8O9Fsj7rnpOGPU9TF7rIbDQvS6nK3P3yvWRHSS9B%2Fimg.jpg%3Fcredential%3DyqXZFxpELC7KVnFOS48ylbz2pIh7yKj8%26expires%3D1756652399%26allow_ip%3D%26allow_referer%3D%26signature%3Dbiznfx4KZ3fUbcoA%252BxCjX4uMWy8%253D&#34; alt=&#34;formatNum_normal&#34; title=&#34;formatNum_normal&#34;/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Change to a normal number format.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;[yes - with right padding(accounting)] #,##0_-;[Red]-#,##0_-;-_-&lt;br&gt;&#xA;[no - without right padding] #,##0;[Red]-#,##0;-&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;formatnum_thousand&#34;&gt;&#xA;  formatNum_thousand&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#formatnum_thousand&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&amp;amp;fname=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.kakaocdn.net%2Fdna%2FbxeuR8%2FbtsPOJgSamJ%2FAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAHkI2iVc3zuNo-HcCn2lcXd4_Pcss-UTjIdTsUtAhKSB%2Fimg.jpg%3Fcredential%3DyqXZFxpELC7KVnFOS48ylbz2pIh7yKj8%26expires%3D1756652399%26allow_ip%3D%26allow_referer%3D%26signature%3DSmHK5ALjVYgT3fZeopyK2pdz7q4%253D&#34; alt=&#34;formatNum_thousand&#34; title=&#34;formatNum_thousand&#34;/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Change in a thousand unit number format.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;[yes - with right padding(accounting)] #,##0,-;[Red]-#,##0,-;-_-&lt;br&gt;&#xA;[no - without right padding] #,##0,;[Red]-#,##0,;-&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;formatnum_mil&#34;&gt;&#xA;  formatNum_mil&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#formatnum_mil&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&amp;amp;fname=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.kakaocdn.net%2Fdna%2FbfBzAg%2FbtsPNkuYTlt%2FAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAGuBYBkFpAPt-sikarJ7kVjwTOkOtZW5W-pyTteCObms%2Fimg.jpg%3Fcredential%3DyqXZFxpELC7KVnFOS48ylbz2pIh7yKj8%26expires%3D1756652399%26allow_ip%3D%26allow_referer%3D%26signature%3D0RJsQTMBaBoyjsPa%252BW%252BesT0Tf4Q%253D&#34; alt=&#34;formatNum_mil&#34; title=&#34;formatNum_mil&#34;/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Change in a million unit number format.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;[yes - with right padding(accounting)] #,##0,,-;[Red]-#,##0,,-;-_-&lt;br&gt;&#xA;[no - without right padding] #,##0,,;[Red]-#,##0,,;-&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
